title.narrative: Procurement of Emergency Obstetric and Neonatal Care Equipment

description.narrative: This activity (Procurement of Emergency Obstetric and Neonatal Care Equipment) is a component of Zambia Maternal Health Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of goods' and a budget of £6,278,249. This component benefits Zambia, and works in the following sector(s): Reproductive health care. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited, DAI Global Health. The start date is 26-06-2009 and the end date is 31-10-2013.
